            "title": "A股開跌   深股現轉升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股低開。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3374點，跌6點或0.18%。現報3378點，跌2點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10157點，跌29點或0.28%。現報10199點，升12點或0.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3898點，跌9點或0.23%。現報3901點，跌6點或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2035點，跌8點或0.39%。現報2047點，升4點或0.22%。</p>\n</div>",
