            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌117點  ADR低水144點   阿里巴巴跌網易升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期跌118點或0.51%，報23272。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市低水144點或0.62%，報23308點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數滑落2.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)收入稍遜預期，美國存託證券(ADS)股價下挫7.6%，較本港低6.2%，報120.89元 ; 網易(09999)績後獲看好，ADR升14.6%，較香港收市價高水14%，折合191.69港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東(09618) ADR較香港收市價低水1%，折合134.02港元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣516.42元，較港收市價較港收市價低0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報91.81元，較香港收市價高1.3% ; 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣375.06元，較香港收市價低0.6% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣65.59元，較香港收市價低0.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211) ADR較香港收市價低水0.6%，折合417,87港元 ; 理想汽車(02015) ADR較香港收市價高水0.1%，折合111.43港元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14933093-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c117%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4144%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e8%b7%8c%e7%b6%b2%e6%98%93%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/HK-STOCK_ADR-1_source-bp_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 08:55:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "荔枝角宇晴軒2房戶778萬成交  原業主2013年買入 帳賺逾1球半",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14931698&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">利嘉閣地產西九龍碧海藍天分行近期促成宇晴軒2座中高層F室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約501方呎，採2房間隔，外望球場景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">業主原叫價800萬元，議價後以778萬元合理價成交，折合實用面積呎價約15529元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，原業主於2013年以約620萬元購入單位，持貨至今沽出，帳面獲利約158萬元，期內物業升值約25%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14931698-%e8%8d%94%e6%9e%9d%e8%a7%92%e5%ae%87%e6%99%b4%e8%bb%922%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6778%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb2013%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%b7%e5%85%a5-%e5%b8%b3%e8%b3%ba%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 08:45:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息大多反彈　1個月拆息回升至1.35厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14930704&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息大多回升，但升幅有限。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">1個月拆息反彈2.1個基點，結束7日跌勢，升至1.35厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜拆息升至約0.058厘，3個月拆息升至約2.12厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">只有兩星期拆息持續下跌，再跌2.7個基點，報大約0.77厘，連跌8日累計跌3.3厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14930704-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%a4%a7%e5%a4%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e3%80%801%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b31-35%e5%8e%98-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 08:45:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "喜韻708萬元成交 原業主持貨10年帳面獲利約81.5萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14928318&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港置業西九龍深水埗分行日前促成一宗該屋苑的買賣成交，外區客以約708萬元購入2房單位，實用呎價約13992元，屬市價成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述單位為喜韻1座中層C室，實用面積約506平方呎，屬2房間隔，向西南望球場景，單位原業主以730萬元放盤約2星期後獲外區客洽詢，雙方經議價後以708萬元易手，實用呎價約13,992元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資料顯示，業主於2015年1月以約626.5萬元購入上述單位，是次易手，原業主帳面獲利約81.5萬元離場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14928318-%e5%96%9c%e9%9f%bb708%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a810%e5%b9%b4%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2%e7%8d%b2%e5%88%a9%e7%b4%8481-5%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 08:45:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
